OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy and dry at first
OL,6,Ftoday. Cloud will thicken through the
OL,7,Fday with an increasing chance of
OL,8,Fshowery outbreaks of rain. Feeling
OL,9,Fcool under the cloudy skies.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy at first with further
OL,12,Fshowers. Cloud will clear during the
OL,13,Fnight allowing for clear spells to
OL,14,Fdevelop. Turning chilly under the
OL,15,Fclearing skies.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FDry on Wednesday with some
OL,18,Fbright or sunny spells. Feeling chilly
OL,19,Fdespite the sunshine in northerly
OL,20,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
